  <brief_title>A Study of the Safety and Efficacy of Synvisc and Depo-Medrol in Patients With Osteoarthritis of the Hip</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Genzyme, a Sanofi Company</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a clinical study to investigate the safety and efficacy of Synvisc and Depo-Medrol in
      treating patients with osteoarthritis (OA) of the hip.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
